{"tid":389884,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Queen傳記電影《波西米亞狂想曲》釋出Freddie Mercury定裝照","createTime":"2017-09-06T15:32:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-08T12:40:09.000Z","uid":41343,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d58503d75d31acee9f43b1e89b0a9ce40bb4a6f3","tid":389884,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T15:32:30.000Z","msg":"由《X戰警》（X-Men）系列導演布萊恩辛格（Bryan Singer）執導的「皇后合唱團」（Queen）傳記電影《波西米亞狂想曲》（Bohemian Rhapsody）在兩週前確定了四位團員的演出卡司後，即將準備開拍，而今天則率先曝光了首張定裝照。<br />\n<br />\n此片在去年 11 月選定影集《駭客軍團》（Mr. Robot）拉米馬利克（Rami Malek）飾演主唱佛萊迪墨裘瑞（Freddie Mercury），而他回憶起第一次完成化妝與造型後，打開眼睛看到鏡子裡的倒影，讓他深刻感受到這是一個非常堅定的時刻。<br />\n<br />\n以經典名曲為片名的《波西米亞狂想曲》將從皇后合唱團在 1970 年成團後開始說起，直到佛萊迪墨裘瑞因愛滋病併發症過世的六年前在 1985 年的&nbsp;Live Aid 演唱會。拉米馬利克還透露，電影當中的演唱除了會使用佛萊迪的聲音外，也會使用他本人的聲音。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.hypesphere.com/20170906133101_38.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.hypesphere.com%2F20170906133101_38.jpg&h=f0014735&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5f890a1c722539afa9f7183a72db7d5d4e3dbaae","tid":389884,"uid":90045,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T20:30:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4206a6b4ce236010cf382d53f37b935d3a91f441","tid":389884,"uid":21896,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T23:31:51.000Z","msg":"咁鬼似既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5ecfd1ced2d3cfe05ee6d9f4cc49648c72519d7","tid":389884,"uid":126044,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T00:54:26.000Z","msg":"岐視gay 佬之前<br />\n望下Freddie Mercury, 張國榮<br />\n再週望下自己"},{"pid":"5f8c0ff3d6a94d0b40090d8b68b0a01c3b84e8ac","tid":389884,"uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T02:01:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岐視gay 佬之前<br />\n望下Freddie Mercury, 張國榮<br />\n再週望下自己</blockquote><br />\n可唔可以列舉啲未死嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma